(27, 1, 27, 2000, 'Cycling Light', '150 taka off retail price! We specifically designed our own cycling light for your Leopard/Pro. With this 500 lumens cycling light, you''ll be well equipped for your night rides. NOTE: This only works with your Leopard/Pro. Shipping is free if you ordered a Leopard/Pro through Punji', 50, '06', 2017, 'BD', 20),
(28, 1, 27, 5000, 'SpeedX Cycling Suit', 'Show off your biking spirit with our cycling suit which matches your Leopard/Pro.', 30, '11', 2016, ' ', 0),
(29, 1, 27, 10000, 'Leopard | Early Bird', '400$ off from retail price! One ride-ready SpeedX Leopard. Smart Control, Carbon Fiber Frame, Shimano 105, TRP TTV Brakes, Aluminum wheels, Vittoria Rubino tires, and more packed into this bicycle! After the campaign we''ll contact you to get the stats for bike fitting and color options!', 0, '09', 2016, 'IN', 1000),
(30, 1, 28, 20000, 'CoWatch Style Kit', 'Stay in style for any occasion. Choose your watch color + two bands - Metal (Mineral Silver, Carbon Black) and/or Leather (Ink Black, Dark Coffee, Charcoal Gray), with a 40% discount on your second band. Flat Shipping Rate at 800 USD to US, Canada, and China. International flat rate at 2000.', 50, '12', 2016, 'BD', 200),
(31, 1, 28, 30000, 'Early Riser: CoWatch', 'Be one of the first CoWatch Supporters! Purchase the CoWatch at an exclusive one-time price. 35.9% Discount. Flat Shipping Rate at 1000  to US, Canada, and China. International flat rate at $25. Color choice: Carbon Black or Mineral Silver', 0, '02', 2017, 'US', 2000),
(32, 1, 28, 1000, 'Additional Watch Band', 'Style and price that can’t be beat. Purchase a second band - either Leather (Ink Black, Dark Coffee, Charcoal Gray) or Stainless Steel (Carbon Black, Mineral Silver) at a 20.4% discount. Shipping included on any previously purchased CoWatch package.', 0, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(33, 1, 29, 5000, 'Vintage Flipbook', ' \r\nIt’s a throwback! Those who donate $25 will receive a special edition vintage flipbook.', 100, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(34, 1, 29, 10000, 'Ultimate Fan Package', '\r\n\r\nFor being the ultimate fan and an all-star supporter of our campaign, claim a package that includes a company sticker, sticky notes, a pen, and a signed piece of marley studio flooring — all packed inside a fashionable Hubbard Street drawstring bag.', 200, '01', 2018, ' ', 0),
(35, 1, 30, 100, 'In The Loop - Noodles', '\r\n\r\nEncourage me to do this. One euro matters - it buys some delicious chinese noodles accross the street, here in Thailand. And one person that cared matters even more than the noodles. You will receive monthly updates of my progress and a thank you on my website.', 34, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(36, 1, 30, 5000, 'Memory Box', 'I will invite you to dinner to personally deliver a unique and personalized box. You will find there a handcrafted book with a special cover and inserts from my journal and other memories from my trip. You will also find a gift from the trip, brought specially for you with a handwritten letter from me. For your friends, you will get 5 printed books and a voucher worth 500 euro that can be used for an individual counseling program (10 sessions) or attending two workshops.', 50, '02', 2017, 'BD', 200),
(37, 1, 31, 3000, 'EARLY BIRD - Medium Zypr Bag', ' Get the Medium Zypr Bag - Early Bird. We call this “coach bag” as it was designed by coaches to be rugged and durable enough to handle all their travel and storage needs. Get the Medium Zypr Bag + Gratitude Reward + Discounted Shipping. Save 13% on Retail Price + over 50% on shipping.', 0, '10', 2016, 'BD', 45),
(38, 1, 31, 5000, 'EARLY BIRD - Large Zypr Bag', ' EARLY BIRD - Get the Large Zypr Bag. We call this the bag “the Mother Lode” because it holds a lot of balls and gear. This bag is ideal for active families with a lot of gear that needs storing. Get the Large Zypr Bag + Gratitude Reward + Discounted Shipping. Save 20% on Retail Price + over 50% on shipping.', 50, '11', 2016, 'BD', 200),
(39, 1, 31, 8000, '1 Md & 13 Zypr Bags - 1 Sm,Lg', '  \r\nGet a Small, Medium and a Large Zypr Bag + Gratitude Reward, + Discounted Shipping. Save 17% on retail price + over 50% on shipping.', 5, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(40, 1, 31, 10000, '3 Bags + Accessories/1 of each', ' Get a Small, Medium and a Large Zypr Bag + the Zypr Waterproof Pouch, Zypr Cargo Straps, and Zypr Shoulder Pad, + Gratitude Reward, + Discounted Shipping. Save 23% on retail price + over 50% on shipping.', 50, '10', 2016, 'BD', 200),
(41, 1, 32, 40000, 'You''re the Designer', ' \r\nEverything from $2 + $10 + $30 + $50 + 50000 sparks + unique robot set suggested by you and design with the help of one of our designers. You give the idea, you name it and see your creation in game\r\n0 out of 20 claimed', 20, '12', 2016, 'BD', 0),
(42, 1, 32, 4000, 'Gear Up', '\r\n\r\nEverything from $2 + $10 + $30 + Guns and Robots T-shirt + 1 year VIP + your name will be listed in the game credits', 0, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(43, 1, 32, 2000, ' Starter Pack', '\r\n20 Inventory Slots, 1 Common Color, 5 Paint Components, 1 Avatar, 1 Unique player portrait, 50 Actuators, 50 Armor Plates, 50 Armaments, 50 CPU Cores 50 Onboard Integration Modules, VIP Account - 30 days, 2000 Sparks', 0, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(44, 1, 33, 80000, ' Wicked Associate Producer', '\r\nAll the previous non-special perks, and: >> Associate Producer credit in the movie and imdb.com! >> Screenwriting e-books >> Art portfolio analysis from Carl Frank OR screenplay analysis from Coverage Ink >> Lobby card or poster signed by William Shatner & the Malevolent team', 0, '01', 0, 'GB', 56),
(45, 1, 33, 100000, ' Fiendish Co-Producer', '\r\nAll of the above (except Special Perks,) plus: You will receive Co-Producer credit on MALEVOLENT (includes imdb.com.) Plus: 1-year mentorship and unlimited development with www.coverageink.com. ', 1, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(46, 1, 33, 800000, ' Bloodcurdling Exec Producer', '\r\nWelcome to the inner circle. All of the above (INCLUDING Special Perks,) plus: Executive Producer credit on MALEVOLENT (includes imdb.com.) Join our creative team and be a part of all MALEVOLENT strategy meetings moving forward. Includes invitation to Hollywood premiere and festival screenings. PLUS: One of our VFX experts will blow you up, cut you in half or treat you to an otherwise ghastly demise. Imagine your friends'' reactions when you post THIS!', 1, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(47, 1, 33, 10000, 'Unique DEADPOOL Statue', ' \r\nWhoa! A stunning, one-of-a-kind piece. 12-inch resin model of Deadpool designed, painted and customized by master modelmaker Francis Gray. Sculpt by Mike Baldwin. original run of 150, now discontinued. Gray added additional weaponry and kit, a swivel head and more. See the 360-degree video on our main page for more. US Shipping and handling included (International additional.) Only one available - grab it fast! Includes Malevolent DVD signed by the creators upon release.', 0, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(48, 1, 34, 5000, 'Animated Character Design', ' \r\n3D Character Design of you, your kid, or a character you’ve been wanting designed', 0, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(49, 1, 34, 6000, 'Get Your Own Theme Song!', ' \r\n3 minute pop song about YOU as your favorite animal or plant character at PACHA JAMMA - the greatest nature festival in history - in the Pacha''s Pajamas story!', 0, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(50, 1, 35, 1000, ' EARLY BIRD - Walletka MINI', '\r\nFor our fastest supporter. 1x Walletka MINI, thread color, leather color and engraving (initials, name or nickname) of your choice. We will ask for information (thread, leather, initials) at the end of the campaign!', 0, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
(51, 1, 35, 5000, ' MINI + CLASSIC', '\r\nCan´t decide whether to buy MINI or CLASSIC? Does having both of them sound the best? Then we''ve got this special PERK for you. 1x Walletka MINI + 1x Walletka CLASSIC, thread color, leather color and engraving (initials, name or nickname) of your choice. We will ask for information (thread, leather, initials) at the end of the campaign!', 50, '08', 2016, ' ', 0),
(52, 1, 36, 5000, '', ' 2-CD Digipack\r\nDeluxe 2-CD Digipack with slipcase & 40 pag. booklet + Signed Photo Card + Guitar Pick + Sticker + Digital download + Your name printed on thanx list. [•••ESPAÑOL•••] 2-CD Digipack de lujo con funda y libreto de 40 pag. + Púa de guitarra + Adhesivo + Foto firmada + Descarga digital + Tu nombre impreso en la lista de agradecimientos.', 0, 'select-month', 0, ' ', 0),
