(30, 4, 'Break Free From University', 'bangladesh', 'GOPALGONJ', 300000, 'A book about self-organized universities & a learning journey to edu projects in 20 countries.', 'images/card_image/x27h0pwsqqlumakiyfx91.jpg', 13, 'book,travel,freedom', 40, '', 'images/video_overlay_image/genxvzklt9zyl8g137em1.jpg', '<h1>\r\n <span 150="" 30.="" a="" africa="" am="" an="" and="" art="" as="" back="" by="" classic="" college="" college.="" deep="" designs="" do="" dr="" experiments="" few="" from="" go="" going="" green="" h="" have:="" i="" in="" india.="" innovative="" institute="" interested="" learning="" like="" list="" masters="" media="" mit="" moldova.="" more="" most="" new="" no="" non-higher-educati of="" olin=""  open="" or="" particularly="" projects="" quest="" radical="" russia="" school="" select="" small="" some="" south="" spend="" springs="" stanford="" stop="" swaraj="" than="" the="" thiel="" to="" traveling="" universities="" university.="" unreas visit="" want="" where="" will="" year="">What do I Need </span></h1>\r\n<p>\r\n <span 150="" 30.="" a="" africa="" am="" an="" and="" art="" as="" back="" by="" classic="" college="" college.="" deep="" designs="" do="" dr="" experiments="" few="" from="" go="" going="" green="" h="" have:="" i="" in="" india.="" innovative="" institute="" interested="" learning="" like="" list="" masters="" media="" mit="" moldova.="" more="" most="" new="" no="" non-higher-educati of="" olin=""  open="" or="" particularly="" projects="" quest="" radical="" russia="" school="" select="" small="" some="" south="" spend="" springs="" stanford="" stop="" swaraj="" than="" the="" thiel="" to="" traveling="" universities="" university.="" unreas visit="" want="" where="" will="" year=""><span><span>For the full version I need roughly 20 flights of 60.000 km, visas for 19 countries on 5 continents, 300 days of food, accommodation and urban transport in 30 cities. All this will get me to the core of this journey: more than 600 beers