(29, 4, 'Help Us Repair the Hubbard Street Dance Center', 'BANGLADESH', 'GOPALGONJ', 500000, 'Our studios have flooded! Hubbard Street Dance Chicago needs your help in repairing our facility. ', 'images/card_image/Indiegogo_Graphic_FINAL_fxk4kv.jpg', 16, 'dance,studio,flood,gopalgonj', 50, '', 'images/video_overlay_image/Chart_V2_jpvvsg.png', '<p>\n <span >On March 14, the sprinkler system in one of our company studios unexpectedly malfunctioned and ran for 40 minutes. Fire trucks rushed to the Hubbard Street Dance Center in response to the alarm, and our building &mdash; which houses the company, administrative offices, the Lou Conte Dance Studio, our costume shop, storage and archives &mdash; was completely evacuated. While fortunately there was no fire, thousands of gallons of water flooded into a large area of our second floor, damaging Studios B, C, and D. More than 50 classes had to be canceled during the following week, while temporary flooring for Studios B and C was secured and installed. We have been working hard to expedite renovations to get the Hubbard Street Dance Center fully up and running again, but the damage is extensive and significant. However, this could be an opportunity to improve multiple aspects of our facility, beyond repairing those affected by the flood &mdash; and that&rsquo;s where you come in!</span></p>\n<br />\n<div>\n <p>\n  &nbsp;</p>\n <p>\n  Many people are asking...</p>\n</div>\n<div>\n <h3>\n  &nbsp;</h3>\n <h1>\n  How Can I Help?</h1>\n <p>\n  To help get us back to serving thousands of students, artists, and audiences each week, we are asking for <i>your</i> help to rebuild the Hubbard Street Dance Center. Our campaign goal is $25,000, which will cover repairs going beyond what was immediately affected by the flood. Donations in any amount are critical in helping us rebuild the Hubbard Street Dance Center, so we may continue fulfilling our mission to change lives through dance.</p>\n</div>\n<h3>\n &nbsp;</h3>\n<h3>\n Where Will the Money Go?</h3>\n<p>\n &nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n &nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n The money raised by this campaign will not only bring our studios back to full functionality, but also better the facilities that are used by hundreds of students, professionals, and teaching artists each day. With your money we will be able to repair ceiling insulation in two studios, add outlets in three studios, upgrade sound systems in all studios, repair our hydraulic lift, upgrade our faculty lounge, replace carpeting and more! &nbsp;Take a closer look:</p>\n<h1>\n Other Ways You Can Help</h1>\n<h3>\n Some people just can&#39;t contribute, but that doesn&#39;t mean they can&#39;t help:</h3>\n<ul>\n <li>\n  Ask folks to get the word out and make some noise about your campaign.</li>\n <li>\n  Remind them to use the Punji share tools!</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n And that&#39;s all there is to it.</p>\n', 1, '2016-04-26 23:04:57', '', 's', 'p', 'sp@gmail.com', 1),
(32, 4, 'Guns and Robots Full Blast', 'BANGLADESH', 'GOPALGONJ', 500000, 'Guns and Robots is a free to play online third person shooter. ', 'images/card_image/gar_robot2_d5uekh.jpg', 1, 'free to play,online,shooter', 60, '', 'images/video_overlay_image/prk2_fwtymi.jpg', '<p>\r\n <span ><strong>Guns and Robots</strong></span> i<span >s a free to play online third person shooter. The game brings robot action with massive customization. Players get cartoony bright 3D graphics in attractive environments and challenge each other in open arenas. Guns and Robots gives fun, entertaining experience with easy to master gameplay and numerous options to experiment robot constructing skills.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >Official website: <a href="https://play-gar.com/" rel="noopener nofollow" target="_blank">https://play-gar.com/</a><br />\r\n Steam webpage: <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/293540" rel="noopener nofollow" target="_blank">https://store.steampowered.com/app/293540</a></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n  Explain how much funding you need and where it&#39;s going. Be transparent and specific-people need to trust you to want to fund you.</li>\r\n <li>\r\n  Tell people about your unique perks. Get them excited!</li>\r\n <li>\r\n  Describe where the funds go if you don&#39;t reach your entire goal.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div  550px;">\r\n <span ><strong>Massive customization.</strong> In Guns and Robots, the robots come in three module classes based on players&#39; assembly and unlimited options for character customization.</span></div>\r\n<div  left;">\r\n <span ><img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1460375332/bullet1_eotboc.jpg"  /></span></div>\r\n<p>\r\n <br />\r\n <br />\r\n <br />\r\n &nbsp;</p>\r\n<div  550px;">\r\n <span ><strong>Pinpoint enemies with multiple weapons simultaneously.</strong> Wide variety of potential combinations per weapon allows players to fine&mdash;tune their arsenal according to their game play preferences.</span></div>\r\n<div  left;">\r\n <span ><img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1460375332/bullet1_eotboc.jpg"  /></span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div  550px;">\r\n <span ><strong>Enjoyable and extremely funny online arenas</strong> where players literally blast their way through.</span></div>\r\n<div  left;">\r\n <span ><img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1460375332/bullet1_eotboc.jpg"  /></span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div  550px;">\r\n <span ><strong>Adrenaline-pumping game play.</strong> Different maps add fine mixture of thrill, speed and action to the game play.</span></div>\r\n<div  left;">\r\n <span ><img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1460375332/bullet1_eotboc.jpg"  /></span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div  550px;">\r\n <span ><strong>Dynamic combat experience.</strong> Players can choose to line up for high-level real-time combat.</span></div>\r\n<div  left;">\r\n <span ><img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1460375332/bullet1_eotboc.jpg"  /></span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div  550px;">\r\n <span ><strong>Player Guilds.</strong> Players can join, create guilds and benefit from numerous guild features.</span></div>\r\n<div  left;">\r\n <span ><img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1460375332/bullet1_eotboc.jpg"  /></span></div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div  550px;">\r\n <span ><strong>Achievements.</strong> Variety of achievements for the players with exceptional performance.</span></div>\r\n', 1, '2016-04-27 02:04:42', '', 'sukanto', 'bala', 'sukantobala@gmail.com', 1),
(33, 4, 'MALEVOLENT: The Animated Horror Film', 'BANGLADESH', 'GOPALGONJ', 5000000, 'Help us finish the first Bangladeshi animated horror film - starring genre luminaries! ', 'images/card_image/cokvh8zupipwmult1exr.png', 2, 'horror,animation,horrorfilm', 0, '', 'images/video_overlay_image/dvcl4uat6aehivg9djue.png', '<p>\r\n <span ><span ><b>MALEVOLENT</b></span> is about a young woman named Miriam DeKalb (<b>Dani Lennon</b>, FearNet/Machinima&#39;s BITE ME) who works for a non-profit which promotes global peace initiatives. When her billiionaire sociopath father Cyrus<b> (Ray Wise)</b> learns he is dying, Cyrus calls Miriam and her three siblings together to &quot;discuss his will.&quot; However, what he actually has planned is to <b>pronounce judgment on them all.</b> They are, in his view, traitors, and he has <b>grisly death traps</b> planned for each of them.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >The wrinkle: <b>a race of intergalactic gamblers,</b> who wager on human conflicts as bloody sport, have chosen Miriam as their protagonist for this match. Thus the entire situation is being manipulated by the Gamemaster <b>(Morena Baccarin,)</b> who has the power to reverse time and reconfigure events as they play out. And so the playing field is constantly changing under Miriam&#39;s feet -- sometimes to her benefit, but usually, not. Through it all, The Overseer <b>(William Shatner)</b> calls the game. </span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span ><b>MALEVOLENT </b>means everything to us. Our core team has literally been working on this project for years, giving it our all. Animated movies generally require <b>millions of dollars</b>. Yeah, well, we don&#39;t have millions. But we have heart. And we have talent and passion and geek fighting spirit! We&#39;ve put together an international team of <b>21 artists and colorists, </b>many of whom who have been working on this project for over a year. There&#39;s a lot on the line for all of us, but we are heartened by the support we&#39;ve received thus far, and the reactions we&#39;ve gotten at places like <b>Stan Lee&#39;s Comikaze Expo</b>, where we did a panel and screened work-in-progress footage.</span></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<h1>\r\n <span >Where does all the money go?</span></h1>\r\n<p>\r\n <span ><b>Making a hand-drawn animated movie is expensive!</b> We have been in production for a year, and we are about 7-8 months away from completion -- but our internal financing is running low.&nbsp; <b>We need your help. </b>We need to raise money for:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Additional artists/animators</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Sound Mixing</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Color Correction</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Music</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Scoring</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Festival Submissions</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >And the list goes on...</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >We have worked so hard on this project, and <b>with your generosity</b>, we can make it to the finish line!</span></p>\r\n', 1, '2016-04-27 02:04:44', '', 'sukanto', 'bala', 'sukantobala@gmail.com', 1),
(34, 4, 'Animated Book... What''s That?', '', '', 50000, 'Augmented Reality App brings Environmental Children''s Book to Life, inspires Youth Leaders Worldwide ', 'images/card_image/qlizurkpxjkmjmjqvpj0.jpg', 3, 'DREAM,ANIMATION,BOOK', 0, '', 'images/video_overlay_image/nflgnuncd133lpncdz5q.jpg', '<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >We need a minimum of $5K to finish the development of the app.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >If we get $10K, we will add some more features to the app including the capability to take a selfie with Pacha and hire a couple of young people to do outreach for the best seller campaign. If we get more than $10K, we will put it into he bestseller campaign.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >If we don&#39;t reach our entire goal, whatever funds we get will be used to make the best app we can.</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Be the first to get the new Pacha&#39;s Pajamas Animated Book. Our unique perks include 20 signed Pre-Release copies of Pacha&#39;s Pajamas that you will have before the April 5th publishing date.&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >We also are offering the opportunity to be made into a cartoon character and even be in a short animation with Pacha.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>\r\n The Impact</h1>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Our Animated Book inspires kids and families to discover their unique gifts and bring them to the world. It encourages them to explore their connection with the natural world and to create the world they want to live in. It also models youth leadership and climate action.</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >The Pacha&#39;s Pajamas music in the Animated Book has won 9 awards.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h1>\r\n Risks &amp; Challenges</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >Our biggest risk is selecting an developer that is unable to deliver in time for the launch. To mitigate this risk, we are going through a rigorous selection process with support from the service Upwork.com.</span></p>\r\n<h1>\r\n Other Ways You Can Help</h1>\r\n<br />\r\n<ol>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Join our <a href="https://www.thunderclap.it/projects/38699-animated-book-what-s-that" rel="noopener nofollow">Thunderclap campaign</a> to get the word out.</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Send an email to your circle of friends sharing the campaign and/or sing them to pre-order the animated book. I will send you a blurb. &nbsp;</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span ><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Pachas-Pajamas-Written-Nature-Morgan/dp/1630477044/ref=sr_1_1" rel="noopener nofollow">Pre-order the Animated Book on Amazon</a> or another online retailer before April 12th</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Connect us with infuential people and organizations that may want to support the launch&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span >Please get the word out and make some noise about our campaign using the Indiegogo share tools!</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <ul>\r\n   <li>\r\n    <span ><span  0px;"><b>What is the problem you are solving?</b>&nbsp;Most Children&#39;s Entertainment is mental junk food. It may satisfy cravings but it is making kids sick.</span></span></li>\r\n   <li>\r\n    <span ><span  0px;"><b>Why should I support this project?</b>&nbsp;This project aims to catalyze a shift towards &quot;nutritious&quot; children&#39;s&nbsp;entertainment&nbsp;that supports the healthy social and emotional development of today&#39;s children. Our vision is for all kids to have access to mind blowing, culturally-relevant, age-appropriate entertainment as they develop into young adults.&nbsp; </span></span></li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n </li>\r\n</ol>\r\n', 1, '2016-04-27 02:04:43', '', 'sukanto', 'bala', 'sukantobala@gmail.com', 1),
(35, 4, 'Black Chilli leather wallet', '', '', 160000, 'Hand-stitched leather mini wallet with personal initials for everyday using! ', 'images/card_image/IMG_4403_kjx95m.jpg', 18, 'LATHER,WALET,HANDMADE', 30, '', 'images/video_overlay_image/IMG_4112b_zqoz2e.jpg', '<h1>\r\n What are you going to get for your support?</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n <span ><b>Walletka MINI</b></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- capacity for <b>5</b> cards + cash</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- hand-waxed thread</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- laser cut (perfect cut accuracy)</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- hand-stitched</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- high-quality Italian leather</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- engraved initials, nickname or name on the front side (up to <b>15 characters</b>)</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- your personal choice of the thread color</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- 3 color options of the leather (space gray,&nbsp;cognac brown and midnight blue)</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >Do you need more space for credit cards? Then your perfect choice is Walletka classic.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span ><b>Walletka CLASSIC&nbsp;</b></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- capacity for <b>10 cards</b> + cash</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- hand-waxed thread</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- laser cut (perfect cut accuracy)</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- hand-stitched</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- high-quality Italian leather</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- engraved initials, nickname or name on the front side (up to <b>25 characters</b>)</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- your personal choice of the thread color</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >- 3 color options of the leather (cognac brown, midnight blue and space gray)</span></p>\r\n', 1, '2016-04-27 02:04:46', '', 'sukanto', 'bala', 'sukantobala@gmail.com', 1),
(37, 1, 'BLTouch : Auto Bed Leveling Sensor for 3D Printers', 'BANGLADESH', 'laxmipur', 500000, 'Sensor for 3D', 'images/card_image/In_Install_adqeqk.jpg', 17, 'SENSOR,TECHNOLOGY,3D', 0, '', 'images/video_overlay_image/In_Cutter2_nmwzpi.jpg', '<p>\r\n <span  30px;letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 24px;"><img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1461421616/In_Summary_gpxsgb.jpg"  0px;font-family: ''Benton Sans'', Helvetica, sans-serif;max-width:620px;" /></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span  30px;letter-spacing: 0px;font-size: 24px;"><img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1461424975/In_P01A_iasnnt.jpg"  /></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span ><span  0px; font-family: "Benton Sans",Helvetica,sans-serif;">BLTouch is an auto leveling sensor for 3D Printers based on open-source.&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span ><span  0px; font-family: "Benton Sans",Helvetica,sans-serif;">Simple, Smart, High-precision</span></span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span ><span  0px; font-family: "Benton Sans",Helvetica,sans-serif;">It could work with any kinds of bed materials, such as glasses, woods, metals, and so on.</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >Simple, Smart, High-precision<br />\r\n It could work with any kinds of bed materials, such as glasses, woods, metals, and so on.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1461421635/In_Features_khilec.jpg"  /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n Main functions and controls of BLTouch are same as usual auto bed leveling sensor, consists of RC servo and micro switch.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n <b>Thus, BLTouch can be applied on almost every board.</b></p>\r\n<p>\r\n BLTouch fulfilled simple structure and high precision by using progressively designed solenoid and hall sensor, and aimed user convenience and enjoyable printing by adding many smart functions, self-test, alarm, alarm release, test mode for M119.</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n <span  0px;">&nbsp; Simple</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n  <h4>\r\n   <span  0px;font-family: "Benton Sans", Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight: normal;">BLTouch can be easily applied, since it has a small and simple structure.&nbsp;</span><span  0px;font-family: "Benton Sans", Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight: normal;">Gathering information &amp; firmware setting will be an easy task, because BLTouch works as usual auto bed leveling sensor.</span></h4>\r\n </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>\r\n <span  0px;">&nbsp;Smart</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n  <h4>\r\n   <span  0px;font-family: "Benton Sans", Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight: normal;">Self-test : The push pin is operated three times to test when the power is on</span></h4>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span  0px;font-family: "Benton Sans", Helvetica, sans-serif;font-weight: normal;">Alarm : The LED light blinks if a problem found on a self-test or on an operation</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>\r\n <span  0px;">&nbsp; High-precision&nbsp;</span></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span  0px;font-family: "Benton Sans", Helvetica, sans-serif;">BLTouch&rsquo;s Standard Deviation in repeatability is around 0.005mm, at that precise.&nbsp;</span><span  0px;font-family: "Benton Sans", Helvetica, sans-serif;">&nbsp;(refer to attached video)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n <img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1461413761/BLTouch_table001_w87zmw.jpg"  /><span>※ The data above can be varied by assembling shape and other environments.</span></p>\r\n', 1, '2016-04-27 02:04:45', '', 'sajan', 'poddar', 'sajanpoddar@gmail.com', 1),
(38, 1, 'SOS: Shout of Survival', '', '', 500000, 'A multi-player SHOUTING game where 2 monsters hunt down 2 humans that are trying to reunite. ', 'images/card_image/MonsterAll_g7dtg1.png', 1, 'HORROR,SHOTING,MULTIPLAYER', 0, '', 'images/video_overlay_image/finishing_move_ynfntj.jpg', '<p>\r\n <span  ''Benton Sans'', Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-weight: normal;letter-spacing: 0px;line-height: 26px;background-color: initial;">SOS: Shout Of Survival is being developed for the PC and MAC with gamepad support (of course!), and will be made available through Steam. Other platforms, like Linux, are considered but are not a high priority.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n In the darkness with minimum vision, Humans shout out to each other. They will know their corresponding location by hearing and following the sound direction.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n However! The monsters will also hear them and will run to the humans before they reunite as they can also hear them.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n The Monsters have a constant scary sound ongoing, so humans will be able to hear monsters incoming and will be able to also assess the direction from their scary sound.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n The Monsters have a special ability where they can HIDE their voice for few seconds, AND THIS IS WHERE IT IS FUN for the monsters. As soon as they think they are approaching a human, they can hide their sound and close in to the humans to give them the scare (and death) or their lives!</p>\r\n<div>\r\n <p>\r\n  <img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1460599761/BrokenMonster_ea3ard.png"  327.242px;height: 201px;max-width:620px;" /></p>\r\n <span>We&rsquo;d like to note that this project is a Fixed Funding project. Which means that we either reach our goal and take it all or fail and leave empty handed. So we really need your support to make this happen.</span></div>\r\n<p>\r\n <img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1460599830/GreenLightLove_lk5ukm.png"  372.651px;height: 229px;max-width:620px;" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span><a href="http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=665484362" rel="noopener nofollow" target="_blank">We would also love your support in getting the game greenlit on Steam, please go there and support our game to be greenlit!</a></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n Link:&nbsp;<a href="http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=665484362" rel="noopener nofollow" target="_blank">http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetai...</a></p>\r\n', 1, '2016-04-27 02:04:54', '', 'sajan', 'poddar', 'sajanpoddar@gmail.com', 1),
(39, 1, 'Headkayse -A game changer in cycle helmet safety', '', '', 5000000, 'World''s 1st multi-impact, one-size-fits-all, foldable cycle helmet. It''s time for a change. ', 'images/card_image/Headkayse_Intro_01.gif', 17, 'SPORT,TECHNOLOGY', 0, '', 'images/video_overlay_image/Headkayse_Intro_01.gif', '<p>\r\n <span >What is Headkayse?</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span ><em><strong>Headkayse is a revolutionary new helmet technology, design, and approach.</strong></em></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >We started with the challenge of creating a better folding helmet. But this quickly led us to completely rethink the design of cycle helmets, forcing us to develop our own our unique, safer, rugged, soft material &#39;Enkayse&#39; to replace traditional Expanded Polystyrene EPS.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >The resulting Headkayse One is not only the simplest and most compact folding helmet possible, it&#39;s also a better all round helmet for cyclists.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >Whatever, type of cycling you do, wherever you go - &#39;The One&#39; Offers you:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span ><strong>INCREASED SAFETY</strong> - The world&#39;s first multiple-impact protection helmet, which conforms to world safety standards.</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span ><strong>TOUGHNESS!</strong> - Throw it on the floor, in a bag, wherever - it&#39;s fine. No more worrying about every small knock to your expensive but fragile helmet.</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span ><strong>ONE SIZE THAT FITS ALL</strong> - the flexibility &amp; patented adjustment system give the Headkayse unprecedented ability to fit any size of head, from children to large adults. It even quickly adapts to woolly hats!</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span ><strong>AMAZING COMFORT</strong> - Whatever shape your head is (we&#39;re all different!) Headkayse will adjust &amp; mould to your head, quickly feeling incredibly comfy and secure.</span></li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <span ><strong>CUTTING EDGE STYLING</strong> - Carefully crafted to blend the best helmet shapes that suit the human head - Headkayse looks surprisingly good on all people. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<h2>\r\n Why do I need a flexible Helmet?</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >Headkayse embraces individuality. Because of its flexibility, and our patented adjustment system, the helmet simply just adapts to your head shape, making it more comfortable, fit more securely and&nbsp;look more compact.&nbsp; For the first time since the days of leather helmets in the 1930&rsquo;s, a cycle helmet conforms to your head shape. And it&#39;s truly one size fits ALL, need we say more?</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >OK nothing personal but let&#39;s be honest, cycle helmets are pretty strange looking things on most people. Aerodynamic wedges for roadies are great if you&#39;re in the Tour de France, but a bit weird when yoou&#39;re just poppping to the shops. The &#39;skate park bowl&#39; looks great on a dude with a BMX, but a bit suspect on a middle aged commuter.</span></p>\r\n', 1, '2016-04-27 02:04:47', '', 'sajan', 'poddar', 'sajanpoddar@gmail.com', 1),
(40, 1, 'Kamibot - Robot Teaches Your Kids to Code', '', '', 500000, 'Kamibot is a programmable papercraft robot that kids can customize with their own code and skins. ', 'images/card_image/fzp2jaedyxn2ebxmoixk.png', 13, 'CODING,robots,learning', 57, '', 'images/video_overlay_image/d7ifb1pep6etjfrk8gxz.png', '<p>\r\n <span >Coding is an important skill for kids to learn. But unless parents and educators can make it fun, kids are never going to stick with it.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >We&rsquo;ve created Kamibot to be a small, programmable robot that kids can endlessly customise by writing their own code, and by adding creative papercraft skins.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >Kamibot is more than just an educational robot. You can also control Kamibot with a smartphone or tablet. This is crucial because kids get to know Kamibot as a toy and see its full range of capabilities before they start to program it themselves.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n <img src="https://c1.iggcdn.com/indiegogo-media-prod-cld/image/upload/c_limit,w_620/v1458524979/fsxlq5v8ya7ywhxhesuv.png"  /></p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n <span >With the included app, you can control Kamibot with your Android or iOS smartphone or Tablet. You can easily control Kamibot&rsquo;s direction, speed, the direction of its head, and the color if its LED lights.</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span >Kamibot doesn&rsquo;t need constant supervision to know what to do. You can use the app to put it in line mode and Kamibot will use the IR sensors on its undercarriage to follow a black line on the ground through complex obstacle courses you create.</span></p>\r\n', 1, '2016-04-27 02:04:49', '', 'sajan', 'poddar', 'sajanpoddar@gmail.com', 1),
(41, 1, 'To Catch a Macaw', '', '', 200000, 'A film about biologist Erica Pacífico and her brave efforts to protect the Lear''s Macaw in Brazil. ', 'images/card_image/hvzgx1mr0vlgs5dprbwp.jpg', 2, 'film,biology', 0, '', 'images/video_overlay_image/zuacjfn9fm3dxr2sjtl3.png', '<h3>\r\n What We Need &amp; What You Get</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n Up until now, the project has been self-funded. Part of the needed material was either already bought with our own efforts, hired from Angela&#39;s university or kindly lent by friends.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n We&#39;re now at a point where we need to supplement funds, mostly for the shoot. Here&#39;s the breakdown:</p>\r\n<p>\r\n <span  0px;font-size: 24px;font-weight: bold;">The Impact</span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n Thirty years ago, the exquisite Lear&rsquo;s Macaw was on the brink of extinction - there were only 70 known birds left in the wild. Since then, amazing work has been carried out by Biodiversitas along with local people and researchers such as Erica. Working together to help conserve the species, they&rsquo;ve achieved astonishing results: numbers have increased from a few dozen in the late 1980s to about 1300 today.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n In October 2016, when &#39;To Catch a Macaw&#39; is completed, it will be screened at the BBC headquarters in Bristol, UK. The plan is to then enter the documentary into conservation film festivals around the world so we can share this success story far and wide. Also, in order to reach the local people living in close proximity to these amazing birds, a future campaign will advocate for a screening in Canudos, Brazil.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n Our biggest expenses will be:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n <li>\r\n  <p>\r\n   getting both crew members on location;</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <p>\r\n   paying for equipment insurance;</p>\r\n </li>\r\n <li>\r\n  <p>\r\n   arranging other much needed equipment such as solar panels and a small generator.</p>\r\n </li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>\r\n Overloading the responsibilities of production management, camerawork and sound recording onto one person would affect the potential quality of the film. To avoid this risk, it&#39;s important that C&eacute;sar and Angela work as a team.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n Bringing cameras, lenses, gadgets and computers on location always involves risks of theft and damage. Although we take great precautions to ensure the safety of our equipment, we can&#39;t go without insurance for it all. Unfortunately, this will take a large chunk of our budget.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n Since we&#39;ll be camping and shooting in a remote location, there will be no electricity to charge our equipment. A few items can be charged in the vehicle, but to guarantee that our entire kit is fully powered and ready to shoot on schedule we&#39;ll need solar panels and a small generator. Just imagine how AMAZING it would be to power our documentary shoot entirely on a renewable energy resource!!! With your help we can make it happen!!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n <img height="144" src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/Ik1dqViLfwrtRhUbUptgS15049BAZZdGS7WCWmc4e1Sf2mdazzHmmGCPdjm6u7DtvZ8kBa7FFhMHutmx-IlUr9_X8iiDPpMoOkU2tZF3Saf8OSJgay-HB29ZjXnjcFvQL37IRblQ"  271.981px;height: 186px;max-width:620px;" width="211" /></p>\r\n', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', '', '', '', 0);
